OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThalidomide survivors in   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FScotland to get lifelong   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsupport                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thalidomide survivors living in        
OL,6, Scotland will receive lifelong         
OL,7, financial support, the Scottish        
OL,8, government has announced.              
OL,10,FHealth Secretary Humza Yousaf said he  
OL,11,Fhoped the commitment to provide grants 
OL,12,Fwould reassure those affected.         
OL,14,FThere are 50 known survivors of the    
OL,15,Fbanned pregnancy drug living in        
OL,16,FScotland, most now in their 60s.       
OL,18,FThey are among thousands born with limb
OL,19,Fdeformities after their mothers took   
OL,20,Fthalidomide while pregnant.            
